* &quot;Tevye&#x27;s Monologue&quot; – Tevye
* &quot;Miracle of Miracles&quot; – Motel
* &quot;Tevye&#x27;s Dream&quot; – Tevye, Golde, Grandma Tzeitel, Rabbi, Fruma-Sarah and Company
* &quot;Sunrise, Sunset&quot; – Tevye, Golde, Perchik, Hodel and Company
