===River Thurne===

The River Thurne is a tributary of the River Bure. It rises near Martham Broad and flows for about to Thurne Mouth where it joins the Bure. It is wide open and windswept, and on its way it flows through or passes:

*Upper Thurne Broads and Marshes Site of Special Scientific Interest
*Hickling Broad
*Hickling
*Horsey
*Horsey Mere
*Martham Broad (NNR) (national nature reserve)
